data.description: ***$15,000 PRICE IMPROVEMENT***Charming Rose Park Gem! Welcome to 1297 Garnette St, a beautifully maintained home in the coveted Rose Park area of Salt Lake City, UT.  This delightful 5 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence offers a perfect blend of classic charm and modern convenience.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the stunning original floors that have been meticulously renovated and fresh Paint throughout.  New electrical panels both inside and outside (Feb. 2023). 2 stunning fireplaces upstairs and downstairs! The Level Brick construction of this home adds durability and timeless appeal to the property. Did I mention a 2 car detached garage!  Location is key, and this home boasts an unbeatable one.  10 minutes drive to downtown Salt Lake City, quick access to all the shopping, dining, and entertainment.  Commuting is a breeze with easy access to I-15 and I-215, each 5 minutes away! Additionally the Salt Lake International Airport is a mere 15 minutes from this home.  For those who enjoy outdoor activities, Rose Park Golf Course, parks, and playgrounds are also a few minutes away . Schedule a Showing today!   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from __county____________ .  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
